{"paragraphs":[{"cues":[{"time":2585,"text":"What do you see?"},{"time":5888,"text":"Most of you see a barbershop,"},{"time":8792,"text":"but I see an opportunity:"},{"time":11704,"text":"an opportunity for health,"},{"time":14453,"text":"an opportunity for health equity."}]},{"cues":[{"time":18112,"text":"For black men, the barbershop\nis not just a place"},{"time":21826,"text":"where you get your hair cut\nor your beard trimmed."},{"time":25328,"text":"No, it's much more than that."},{"time":28465,"text":"Historically, the barbershop\nhas been a safe haven for black men."},{"time":33364,"text":"It's a place where we go for friendship,"},{"time":36594,"text":"solidarity and solace."},{"time":40094,"text":"It's a place where we go\nto get away from the stress"},{"time":43711,"text":"of the grind of work"},{"time":46982,"text":"and sometimes home life."},{"time":50241,"text":"It's a place where we don't have to worry"},{"time":52226,"text":"about how we're being perceived\nby the outside world."},{"time":56233,"text":"It's a place where we don't\nfeel threatened,"},{"time":59566,"text":"or threatening."},{"time":63082,"text":"It's a place of loyalty and trust."},{"time":66335,"text":"For that reason,"},{"time":68502,"text":"it's one of the few places\nwhere we can fearlessly be ourselves"},{"time":72425,"text":"and just ... talk."},{"time":76533,"text":"The talk, the shop talk, the conversation,"},{"time":79558,"text":"that is the essence\nof the black barbershop."}]},{"cues":[{"time":83178,"text":"I can remember going to the barbershop\nwith my dad as a kid."},{"time":87134,"text":"We went to Mr. Mike's barbershop\nevery other Saturday."},{"time":91530,"text":"And like clockwork,\nthe same group of men would be there"},{"time":95221,"text":"every time we went,"},{"time":96966,"text":"either waiting on their favorite barber"},{"time":99347,"text":"or just soaking up the atmosphere."}]},{"cues":[{"time":103321,"text":"I can remember the jovial greeting\nthat warmly welcomed us"},{"time":107193,"text":"every time we went."}]},{"cues":[{"time":109677,"text":"\"Hey Rev,\" they would say to my dad."},{"time":113726,"text":"He's a local pastor,\nand they treated him like a celebrity."}]},{"cues":[{"time":117923,"text":"\"Hey young fella, how you doing?\""},{"time":120266,"text":"they would say to me,"},{"time":121742,"text":"making me feel just as special."}]},{"cues":[{"time":125118,"text":"I remember the range\nof the conversations was immense."},{"time":130173,"text":"The men would talk about politics\nand sports and music"},{"time":135205,"text":"and world news, national news,"},{"time":138776,"text":"neighborhood news."},{"time":141064,"text":"There was some talk about women"},{"time":144387,"text":"and what it was like to be\na black man in America."},{"time":148585,"text":"But many times they also\ntalked about health."},{"time":153171,"text":"The conversations about health\nwere lengthy and deep."},{"time":157395,"text":"The men often recounted\ntheir doctor's recommendations"},{"time":160608,"text":"to cut salt in their diet"},{"time":162723,"text":"or to eat less fried foods"},{"time":165468,"text":"or to stop smoking"},{"time":167713,"text":"or to reduce stress."},{"time":169911,"text":"They talked about the different ways\nyou could reduce stress,"},{"time":173356,"text":"like simplifying one's love life --"}]},{"cues":[{"time":176378,"text":"(Laughter)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":180866,"text":"all ways to treat high blood pressure."}]},{"cues":[{"time":185585,"text":"There's a lot of talk about\nhigh blood pressure in the barbershop."},{"time":190261,"text":"That's because almost 40 percent\nof black men have it."},{"time":196140,"text":"That means that almost\nevery single black man"},{"time":200157,"text":"either has high blood pressure"},{"time":202123,"text":"or knows a black man who has it."}]},{"cues":[{"time":205940,"text":"Sometimes, those conversations\nin the barbershop"},{"time":209211,"text":"would be about what happens\nwhen high blood pressure"},{"time":211874,"text":"is not adequately addressed."}]},{"cues":[{"time":215318,"text":"\"Say, did you hear about Jimmy?\nHe had a stroke.\""}]},{"cues":[{"time":221612,"text":"\"Did you hear about Eddie?\nHe died last week."},{"time":225891,"text":"Massive heart attack."},{"time":227603,"text":"He was 50.\""}]},{"cues":[{"time":230584,"text":"More black men die from high blood\npressure than from anything else,"},{"time":234527,"text":"even though decades of medical wisdom\nand science have demonstrated"},{"time":239446,"text":"that death from high blood pressure\ncan be prevented"},{"time":242614,"text":"with timely diagnosis\nand appropriate treatment."}]},{"cues":[{"time":247132,"text":"So why is high blood pressure\nso differentially deadly for black men?"},{"time":252457,"text":"Because too often, high blood pressure\nis either untreated"},{"time":256391,"text":"or under-treated in black men,"},{"time":259056,"text":"in part because of our lower engagement\nwith the primary healthcare system."},{"time":264558,"text":"Black men, in particular\nthose with high blood pressure,"},{"time":268363,"text":"are less likely to have\na primary care doctor"},{"time":270491,"text":"than other groups."}]},{"cues":[{"time":272238,"text":"But why?"},{"time":274381,"text":"Some of our earliest research\non black men's health"},{"time":277505,"text":"revealed that for many, the doctor's\noffice is associated with fear,"},{"time":283090,"text":"mistrust,"},{"time":285039,"text":"disrespect,"},{"time":287084,"text":"and unnecessary unpleasantness."},{"time":291074,"text":"The doctor's office is only a place\nthat you go when you don't feel well."},{"time":295902,"text":"And when you do go,\nyou might wait for hours"},{"time":299216,"text":"only to get the run-around"},{"time":301589,"text":"and to be evaluated by\na stoic figure in a white coat"},{"time":306184,"text":"who only has 10 minutes to give you"},{"time":308835,"text":"and who doesn't value the talk."},{"time":313215,"text":"So it's no wonder that some men\ndon't want to be bothered"},{"time":316707,"text":"and skip going to the doctor altogether,"},{"time":320027,"text":"especially if they feel fine."}]},{"cues":[{"time":323402,"text":"But herein lies the problem."},{"time":326328,"text":"You can feel just fine"},{"time":328473,"text":"while high blood pressure ravages\nyour most vital organs."}]},{"cues":[{"time":334834,"text":"This is Denny Moe,"},{"time":337525,"text":"owner of Denny Moe's\nSuperstar Barbershop in Harlem."},{"time":341738,"text":"I've been lucky enough to have Denny\nas my barber for the last eight years."}]},{"cues":[{"time":346540,"text":"He said to me once,"},{"time":348245,"text":"\"Hey Doc, you know,"},{"time":350318,"text":"lots of black men trust their barbers\nmore than they trust their doctors.\""}]},{"cues":[{"time":355879,"text":"This was stunning to me,"},{"time":357961,"text":"at first,"},{"time":359769,"text":"but not so much when you think about it."},{"time":362871,"text":"Black men have been with their\ncurrent barbers"},{"time":365611,"text":"on average as long\nas I've been with Denny,"},{"time":367636,"text":"about eight years."},{"time":369674,"text":"And black men see their barbers\nabout every two weeks."},{"time":374841,"text":"Not only do you trust your barber\nwith your look and with your style,"},{"time":379468,"text":"but you also trust him with your secrets\nand sometimes your life."},{"time":385191,"text":"Denny, like many barbers,\nis more than just an artist,"},{"time":388843,"text":"a businessman and confidant."},{"time":391906,"text":"He's a leader and a passionate advocate\nfor the well-being of his community."},{"time":398969,"text":"The very first time I walked\ninto Denny Moe's shop,"},{"time":401971,"text":"he wasn't just cutting hair."},{"time":404445,"text":"He was also orchestrating\na voter registration drive"},{"time":408222,"text":"to give a voice to his customers\nand his community."}]},{"cues":[{"time":414000,"text":"With this kind of activism,"},{"time":417206,"text":"and community investment\nthat typifies the black barbershop,"},{"time":421467,"text":"of course the barbershop\nis a perfect place"},{"time":425039,"text":"to talk about high blood pressure and\nother health concerns in the community."}]},{"cues":[{"time":429944,"text":"First, the barbershop is not\na medical setting,"},{"time":434118,"text":"and so it doesn't have\nall the negative psychological baggage"},{"time":437387,"text":"that comes along with that."},{"time":439428,"text":"When you're in a barbershop,"},{"time":441507,"text":"you're in your territory,\nand you're among friends"},{"time":444960,"text":"who share your history,"},{"time":447246,"text":"your struggle and your health risks."}]},{"cues":[{"time":451308,"text":"Second, because the barbershop\nis a place of connection,"},{"time":455393,"text":"loyalty and trust,"},{"time":457919,"text":"it's a place where you're more open\nto have a conversation about health"},{"time":461452,"text":"and especially about high blood pressure."},{"time":464165,"text":"After all,"},{"time":465659,"text":"conversations about high blood pressure\nhave all the elements of great shop talk:"},{"time":471017,"text":"stress and high blood pressure,"},{"time":473642,"text":"food and high blood pressure,"},{"time":476196,"text":"relationships and high blood pressure,"},{"time":478857,"text":"and yes, what it's like\nto be a black man in America"},{"time":482816,"text":"and high blood pressure."}]},{"cues":[{"time":485846,"text":"But you can do more than just talk\nabout high blood pressure"},{"time":488942,"text":"in the barbershop."},{"time":490675,"text":"You can concretely take action."},{"time":493915,"text":"Here we have an opportunity to partner\nwith the Denny Moe's of the world"},{"time":498697,"text":"and empower communities\nto address the health inequities"},{"time":502999,"text":"that uniquely affect it."},{"time":505364,"text":"When high blood pressure screening\nexpanded from clinics and hospitals"},{"time":508848,"text":"to communities in the 1960s and '70s,"},{"time":511999,"text":"black physicians like\nDr. Eli Saunders in Baltimore"},{"time":515380,"text":"and Dr. Keith Ferdinand in New Orleans"},{"time":517889,"text":"were at the forefront of bringing\nhealth promotion to community hubs"},{"time":521988,"text":"in urban black neighborhoods."}]},{"cues":[{"time":524409,"text":"These pioneers paved the way\nfor my professional journey"},{"time":528573,"text":"with barbershops and health,"},{"time":530580,"text":"which began in Chicago in medical school."}]},{"cues":[{"time":535372,"text":"The very first research project\nthat I worked on as a medical student"},{"time":538878,"text":"was to help design\nhealthcare interventions"},{"time":541402,"text":"that would appeal to black men."},{"time":544844,"text":"We conducted about a dozen focus groups"},{"time":547751,"text":"with a broad cross-section of black men,"},{"time":551050,"text":"and we learned that for them,"},{"time":553188,"text":"being healthy was as much about\nbeing perceived as healthy"},{"time":557595,"text":"as it was about feeling healthy,"},{"time":559867,"text":"and that feeling good\nwent hand in hand with looking good."},{"time":566009,"text":"This work led to the development\nof Project Brotherhood,"},{"time":569882,"text":"a community clinic founded\nby Dr. Eric Whitaker"},{"time":572811,"text":"that provided tailored\nhealthcare to black men."},{"time":576715,"text":"Part of this tailored care"},{"time":578747,"text":"involved having a barber on the premises"},{"time":581572,"text":"to reward the men who came\nfor needed healthcare"},{"time":585199,"text":"with a free haircut,"},{"time":587188,"text":"to let the men know that we, too,\nvalued how they looked"},{"time":591158,"text":"as well as how they felt,"},{"time":593052,"text":"and that what was important to them\nwas also important to us."}]},{"cues":[{"time":598320,"text":"But while there's only one\nProject Brotherhood,"},{"time":601572,"text":"there are thousands of black barbershops"},{"time":604917,"text":"where the intersection of health\nand haircuts can be cultivated."},{"time":610782,"text":"The next stop on my journey\nwas Dallas, Texas,"},{"time":614178,"text":"where we learned that barbers\nwere not only willing"},{"time":617219,"text":"but fully able to roll up\ntheir sleeves and participate"},{"time":621282,"text":"in delivering needed health services\nto improve the health of their customers"},{"time":626830,"text":"and their community."},{"time":628916,"text":"We teamed up with an amazing\ncadre of black barbers"},{"time":632413,"text":"and taught them how\nto measure blood pressure"},{"time":634581,"text":"and how to counsel their customers"},{"time":636386,"text":"and refer them to doctors"},{"time":638237,"text":"to help manage high blood pressure."},{"time":640977,"text":"The barbers were not only willing to do it"},{"time":643263,"text":"but they were damn good at it."},{"time":645794,"text":"Over a three-year period,"},{"time":647772,"text":"the barbers measured\nthousands of blood pressures"},{"time":650740,"text":"resulting in hundreds of black men\nbeing referred to doctors"},{"time":655565,"text":"for medical care\nof their high blood pressure."},{"time":659232,"text":"These barber-doctor partnerships"},{"time":662168,"text":"resulted in a 20 percent increase\nin the number of men"},{"time":666676,"text":"who were able to achieve\ntarget blood pressure levels"},{"time":669493,"text":"and a three-point drop, on average,"},{"time":671977,"text":"in the blood pressure of each participant."},{"time":674421,"text":"If we were to extrapolate\nthat three point drop"},{"time":677413,"text":"to every single black man\nwith high blood pressure in America,"},{"time":680842,"text":"we would prevent 800 heart attacks,\n500 strokes and 900 deaths"},{"time":687113,"text":"from high blood pressure"},{"time":688995,"text":"in just one year."}]},{"cues":[{"time":692802,"text":"And our experience with barbershops\nhas been no different in New York City,"},{"time":697048,"text":"where my journey has currently led me."},{"time":699722,"text":"With an incredible team\nof diverse research assistants,"},{"time":703690,"text":"community health workers and volunteers,"},{"time":706840,"text":"we've been able to partner\nwith over 200 barbershops"},{"time":710265,"text":"and other trusted community venues"},{"time":712773,"text":"to reach over 7,000 older black men."},{"time":716564,"text":"And we've offered high blood pressure\nscreening and counseling"},{"time":719501,"text":"to each and every one of them."},{"time":721810,"text":"Thanks to Denny Moe"},{"time":723519,"text":"and the myriad other barbers\nand community leaders"},{"time":727146,"text":"who shared the vision of opportunity\nand empowerment"},{"time":732114,"text":"to make a difference in their communities,"},{"time":734844,"text":"we've been able to not only\nlower blood pressure"},{"time":737623,"text":"in our participants,"},{"time":739107,"text":"but we've also been able to impact\nother health indicators."}]},{"cues":[{"time":746300,"text":"So what do you see?"},{"time":749532,"text":"What is your barbershop?"},{"time":753694,"text":"Where is that place for you"},{"time":757574,"text":"where people who are affected\nby a unique problem"},{"time":761123,"text":"can meet a unique solution?"},{"time":765567,"text":"When you find that place,\nsee the opportunity."}]},{"cues":[{"time":770603,"text":"Thank you."}]},{"cues":[{"time":771778,"text":"(Applause)"}]}]}